<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hospital-n">hospital <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'hɒspɪtl/    美 /'hɑːspɪtl/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>医院：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>go to (the) hospital</strong>
去医院</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Tom <strong>was taken</strong> / sent <strong>to hospital</strong>.
汤姆被送进了医院。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-in-the-hospital">(be) in (the) hospital</h3>
<p>1.<strong>住院：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her husband is in hospital.
她丈夫在住院。</p></div>

<p>注: 美式英语习惯在hospital前加定冠词，英式英语则习惯不加定冠词。  </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>In a week, Lucy has already been interviewed by six <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (医院).  （2015 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. hospitals  </p></div>